description: The interplanetary contest storyline continues with The Tick and his unusual teammates trying to overcome some overwhelming odds!
name: Challenge of Champions! Part 2: Electric Boogaloo

description:
The House of M saga continues! First, special investigator of human and mutant affairs Ismael Ortega teams up with Lucas Bishop to take down terrorists from the Human Resistance Movement, beginning with a plot to kill hundreds by sabotaging a glamorous movie premiere! And in New X-Men, the Helions go up against a group of New Mutants from the future! Then, watch as the Exiles return to prime Earth to do battle with Proteus. In House of M: The Day After, the X-Men struggle to pick up the pieces in a world that's changed forever.

Collects Mutopia X #1-5, New X-Men #16-19, Exiles #69-71, House of M: The Day After, and Giant-Size Ms. Marvel #1.
name: House Of M: No More Mutants

volume.name: House of M: No More Mutants

name: Moon-Run!; Out of This World; Worlds End; My Moon

description: The Second Man In Space: Igor Kriss is a Russian Astronaut who was supposed to be the first person in space. When launched into space however he suffered an accident rendering him unconscious. Captain Atom discovered him and saves his life with 1000 units of space vaccine. Once realizing Captain Atom is the first man in space he subsequently realizes he is the second and afterwords he lets his country know live on TV, much to the chagrin of his leaders.
name: The 2nd Man in Space

description:
Billy Goslin the son of Gunner Goslin, (Captain Atom's/Allen Adam) best friend has the power to separate himself while he is sleeping into two persons. One stays asleep while the other is awake. In these incidents he plays with a giant alien bird called Loga that flies in space. It is not known if it is the bird that gives him the power or does it come from Billy himself.

At first no one believes Billy when they tells them about his adventures until one day Billy doesn't wake up. For two days he sleeps until Gunner brings his friend Allen over to help his son. Allen figures out that Billy's story must be true. As such go goes into space to find him as Captain Atom. Billy had talked about the dark side of the moon in great detail giving Captain Atom a place to start. Captain Atom ends up finding Billy and convinces Billy not to leave home for so long.
name: The Little Wanderer

description:
The Wreck of X-44

Captain Allen Adam is test piloting the new X-44 when it is launched into space and explodes. As it turns out the ship was sabotaged by Gerald Mudge. Luckily, Captain Adam is Captain Atom and he is able to survive the crash, rebuild the ship take it back to Earth and capture Mudge

Captain Atom on Planet X

Planet X was created by the United State Air Force in 1960. It is a satellite that orbits the earth with all known weather equipment, Geiger counters and, a missile guidance system. It also takes highly magnified television pictures of any potential military threat around the world. As a spy satellite it drew the attention of enemy nations and was a attacked several times with missiles but Captain Atom deflected all the attacks. As none of the nations knew how their missiles were destroyed it was thought that the satellite had defense systems. This kept the satellite safe from enemy attacks.
name: The Wreck of X-44; Captain Atom on Planet X

description:
Bram Stoker's DRACULA colored for the first time! Bram Stokers legendary novel of gothic horror comes to life in this stunning adaptation by comics legends Roy Thomas and Dick Giordanonewly colored by June Chung. Solicitor Jonathan Harker travels to distant Transylvania and encounters the enigmatic and sinister Count Dracula unearthing dread secrets about his foreign host and his castle. The horror continues in issue #2 as Dracula makes his way to England, setting his sights on Lucy Westenra and Mina Murray, Jonathans fianc, and were introduced to Abraham Van Helsing, the one man who may be able to stop the vampire lords terrifying plans.

Originally serialized in Dracula Lives! #5-8, and later reprinted in Stoker's Dracula #1.
name: Into The Spider's Web; The Female of the Species; And In That Sleep...!
Altas Malandragens

description:
Mark Long & Nick Sagan return to take a planetary revolution across the solar system in the sequel to the hit seriesShrapnel: Aristeia Rising

Consumed with advancing their War of Unity on multiple fronts, the Solar Alliance may be vulnerable to an audacious, high-risk assault on one of their most valued possessions. So rests the hopes of oppressed Helots across the System as a plot against the oldest extraplanetary colony moves forward. Once loyal marines now turned freedom fighters, Captain Narayan, Colonel Rossi and their troops have a golden chance to slow down the enemy war machinebut at what cost?

Life is, once again, like a hurricane here in Duckburg! So you know what that means... DuckTales are back! Gear up for adventure as one of the most cherished, fan-favorite Disney franchises explodes back onto the comics page this June! Join Uncle Scrooge, Donald Duck, Huey, Dewey, Louie, and of course Launchpad McQuack as they solve some mysteries and rewrite some history in an action-packed adventure never before seen in the US!
name: Like A Hurricane Part 1: The Everlasting Coal

description:
In an elementary school classroom, Ghost is tied and bound as a hostage. The leader of the terrorists barges in fully armed and says the soldiers outside are taking positions and to get ready for a fight.

Ghost is shown sneaking into a military base. He locates the barracks and kills Lt. Washington in his sleep.

In a flashback, Ghost locates Simon Riley in his home binds, gags, and beats him for the murders of his mother, brother, and sister-in-law. He is executed and the house is set on fire. Before torching the place Ghost switched dog tags to fake his death.

Lt. Washington's body is discovered the next morning and the base is put on alert. They head to the security room to check the videosurveillance.

In Mexico, two ex-military types are enjoying themselves on vacation. They are ambushed and killed. Ghost learns about this ambush and starts the hunt for the ambushers. He locates the leader and kidnaps him. He is taken to a remote location and tortured for information.
name: Dead Won't Rise

description:
Created by TV and movie star,MICHAEL CHIKLIS!

As Zeus races against time to gather his forces and find the remaining Olympians, the Secretary of Defense puts his dark plan into action! And who are all those zombified people and what are the creatures possessing them? Plus: a familiar face awakens from a coma and wants one thing: Revenge!

The SAVAGE LAND ADVENTURE!--featuring SPEEDBALL! When a Fractal turns a Paleontologist into a Dinosaur (STEGRON!), SPEEDBALL joins the SQUADDIES in the Savage Land to stop him from commanding the Dinosaurs to take over the World! Also, KA-ZAR! PLUS--DR.DOOM sends KLAW out to use his mastery of all sound and vibration to track down missing Fractals--but the SQUADDIES found a sound of their own to combat their villainy in "GOOD VIBRATIONS!"
name: The Savage Land Adventure / Good Vibrations

description:
Two guys are captured by Cobra operatives in the woods. Seven months later they are revived by the Baroness and recruited into a special ops team. They are to correspond with a local crime syndicate to trade arms and uranium.

Elsewhere a Joe team is gathering their forces in an investigation into the rumor of the above cobra team. They sneak close to the Cobra base for some reconnaissance. Shortly thereafter, they organize an attack. The cut power, jam their communications, and attack.

A vicious air and ground battle ensues. Many are wounded and/or killed. The Baroness escapes with the intel.
name: Crimson Reign

volume.name: G.I. Joe vs. Cobra JoeCon Special

description:
Overview

A girlfriend for the Vision? Diplomatic immunity for Thor? It looks like things are finally going right for the Avengers. Unless you count how the Visions girlfriend is a criminal being blackmailed by a brutal villain composed entirely out of diamonds, and his high-flying horrifying crime-lord acquaintance. Its the Avengers vs. Diamondhead & the Owl, with the fate of the Vision at stake!

description: In this exciting junior graphic novel, the boys create a swimming pool full of gelatin and have loads of fun. Until it's accidentally hit with Dr. Doofenshmirtz's latest device, a ray designed to turn everything evil! Phineas and Ferb must find a way to stop the giant gelatin monster and save Candace. Then, the kids head off to England to visit their grandparents, where Candace uses the detective methods of Sherlock Holmes to bust the boys. Elsewhere, Agent P is forced to partner with Agent Double 00, a snooty spy who has little respect for our hero.
name: Volume 1: Nothing But Trouble

volume.name: Phineas and Ferb: Early Comic Reader

description: What happens when the boys accidentally knock a Ufo off its course, causing it to crash in their backyard? And what will Phineas, Ferb, Candace, and Isabella do when they meet its pilot, the adorable Meap? While Candace shows off the cute creature, the others take off in Meap's ship and are captured by Meap's arch rival, the sinister Mitch. It's up to Candace and Meap to defeat Mitch and rescue the three interstellar prisoners!
name: Volume 2: The Chronicles of Meap
